        "description": "Wixar StudioVR is a 360° content gamification authoring tool dedicated to immersive learning. Resulting from more than 4 years of R&D, it allows you to design and customize your VR experiences by adding playful interactions to your 360° photos and videos.\nIdeal for creating Serious Games, interactive Virtual Tours, job discovery, onboarding of new employees...\nSpatialized creation, a Wixar innovation, allows you to design your experience directly in VR. This feature brings more precision on the configuration... And a better appreciation of the rendering (preview mode). You will be able to configure your project in a few minutes only.\nBuilding your experiences with Wixar Studio VR is done in autonomy: the intuitive UX/UI allows you to take control of the tool in a short time.\nThe collaborative mode allows you, if you wish, to work simultaneously on the same project with up to 20 participants. Perfect for co-constructing and validating your productions quickly.",
